criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients over 18 years old;

          -  intubated with a 7.5mm endotracheal tube;

          -  mechanically ventilated.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  upper gastrointestinal bleeding;

          -  hemodynamic instability;

          -  airway bleeding;

          -  previous lung diseases.
